OL,3,CKetamine 'should not' become class A
OL,4,Cdrug, government's expert panel says
OL,6,FThe Advisory Council on the Misuse of
OL,7,FDrugs (ACMD) had been asked by the
OL,8,Fgovernment to consider recommendations
OL,9,Faround making the penalties for those
OL,10,Fusing and dealing drugs harsher -
OL,11,Fbringing Ketamine in line with the
OL,12,Flikes of Cocaine and MDMA.
OL,14,FThis development comes after illegal
OL,15,Fuse of Ketamine, especially amongst
OL,16,Fyoung people, surged to record levels,
OL,17,Fas previous reporting from ITV News
OL,18,Fshows.
