OL,3,CKetamine 'should not' become class A
OL,4,Cdrug, government's expert panel says
OL,6,FThe government will now consider
OL,7,Fwhether to follow with this advice and
OL,8,Fkeep the drug as it is - or reclassify
OL,9,Fit as a Class A.
OL,11,FIt had asked for expert advice after
OL,12,Fillegal use surged to record levels,
OL,13,Fbut the ACMD has said it should remain
OL,14,Fa class B controlled substance.
OL,16,FITV News has previously met teens and
OL,17,Ftheir families impacted by continued
OL,18,Fuse of the drug, which can severely
OL,19,Fimpact a person's bladder - leading to
OL,20,Fsome needing to wear adult nappies as
OL,21,Ftheir bladder capacity shrinks.
