OL,3,CKetamine 'should not' become class A
OL,4,Cdrug, government's expert panel says
OL,6,FThe drug was moved from a Class C to a
OL,7,FClass B in 2014. Since then,
OL,8,FKetamine's use has continued to rise.
OL,10,FSome, including the sister of Drag
OL,11,FStar The Vivienne, who died from a
OL,12,Fcardiac arrest after using the drug
OL,13,Flast year, said it should become a
OL,14,Fclass A - while others who've also
OL,15,Flost loved ones say this wouldn't help
OL,16,F- instead calling for more education
OL,17,Fin schools.
