OL,6,FA government spokesperson told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "Ketamine is an extremely
OL,8,Fdangerous substance and the recent
OL,9,Frise in its use is deeply concerning.
OL,11,F"We are grateful to the Advisory
OL,12,FCouncil on the Misuse of Drugs for
OL,13,Fpublishing their assessment. We will
OL,14,Fnow consider the report carefully and
OL,15,Frespond as a matter of priority."
